dct_title_s: Togoland under U.K. Trusteeship : administrative districts, electoral districts, and local council areas
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by spot heights. Map shows administrative districts constituencies and local councils boundaries. "Apart from the territorial boundary the boundaries shown on the map are unsurveyed and undefined and should be regarded as merely diagrammatic." Original map is filed in the Map/Geospatial Center, a map reproduction is included in companion volume. Relief shown by spot heigts. Map shows international, administrative districts, constituencies, and local councils boundaries.
